    "As mentioned in Section IV, the MMRS-1M dataset is constructed based on diverse and comprehensive RS task-specific datasets.",
    "By unifying all the datasets into a multi-modal conversational format, the training process is optimized, reducing costs and enhancing efficiency.",
    "During the training, we only train an off-the-shelf language model LLaMA-2 [21] and randomly initialized visual projections.",
    "We use the AdamW optimizer (β1, β2) = (0.9, 0.95), a maximum learning rate of 2 × 10 -5, a minimum learning rate of 0.",
    "Scene ClassificationTo evaluate the classification performance, supervised and zero-shot classification assessments are conducted."
